  "contentHtml": "<!-- BEGIN COPYRIGHTED TEXT CHUNK --><html><head></head><body><div class=\"chapter\">\n\n<div class=\"freeverse\">\nJust as a fine <a id=\"thoroughbred\">thoroughbred</a> steed\nstumbling, regains its stance,\nfeeling all the more urgency,\n&amp; draws its burden\n\tundaunted.\n\nIn the same way, remember me:\nconsummate in vision,\na disciple of the Rightly\nSelf-awakened One,\nthe Awakened One's thoroughbred child,\n\t   his son.\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n</body></html>",
